@startuml
title BP-05 - Academic Year and Semester Setup

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|School Administrator|
start
:Create academic year;
:Define start date and end date;
:Create semester records;

|Platform|
:Validate dates do not overlap active periods;
:Validate semester belongs to academic year;

if (Date configuration valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save academic period configuration;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Academic Staff|
:Use academic year and semester for student grouping;

|Finance Officer|
:Use period as billing reference;
stop

note right
Current code status:
Academic period is part of the source of truth scope.
It is not yet a dedicated implemented module in current MVP code.
end note
@enduml
